profile:
Our goal is simple, to provide our customers with the best selection, knowledge and service of tools and machinery in the industry.

Atlas Machinery has been selling machinery, power tools and accessories for over 60 years. We are a third generation family business who prides itself in treating our customers like family. Our primary retail location has always been in the heart of downtown Toronto with a wide selection of products which we continue to expand each day. We also have a large warehouse to help with our fast fulfilment of products to serve our customers.

Atlas is not just a business - Atlas is a family. Atlas has a team of more than a dozen staff members who are knowledgeable and dedicated not only to our products but also to our customers. We believe in partnerships with both our customers and our suppliers. We are internationally known and committed to the success of all our partners.

Our business is constantly evolving, we believe we adapt quickly to market changes and can get fast creative solutions for our customers.  Our pricing strategy is to be fair and also extremely competitive. 

We offer a variety of products such as but not limited to: Woodworking and metal working machinery, Power tools, Cordless tools, Cutting tools (metal, wood, masonry and stone, plastics, etc.), Abrasives, Pneumatic tools and fasteners, Hand tools, Mechanical tools, Clamping and work-holding, Precision tools, Inspection tools, Safety equipment, Tool boxes, pouches, and cool tool clothes. We also sell replacement parts and we can get parts for products made by our vendors (vendors list). If you are not interested in fixing your own tools we can take them in for repair.
name: Atlas Machinery Supply Ltd
